### Get all leads (with default pagination)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leads

### Get leads with filtering and pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leads?status=New&priority=High&page=1&limit=5&sort_by=created_at&sort_order=desc

### Get leads with search
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leads?search=john&company=Tech

### Get a specific lead by ID (replace with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leads/{{leadId}}

### Update a lead (replace with actual ID)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/leads/{{leadId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Qualified",
  "lead_score": 90,
  "notes": "Very interested, scheduled demo for next week",
  "next_follow_up": "2024-02-15T10:00:00.000Z",
  "deal_stage": "Negotiation"
}

### Soft delete a lead (replace with actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/leads/{{leadId}}

### Hard delete a lead (replace with actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/leads/{{leadId}}/hard

### Get lead statistics
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leads/stats

### Bulk update leads
POST http://localhost:3000/api/leads/bulk/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lead_ids": ["lead-id-1", "lead-id-2"],
  "update_data": {
    "assigned_to": "user-id-123",
    "status": "Contacted"
  }
}

### Bulk delete leads
POST http://localhost:3000/api/leads/bulk/delete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lead_ids": ["lead-id-1", "lead-id-2"]
}

